profile: Injectech LLC is a Pacific Northwest specialty repair contracting firm that provides construction and consulting services to commercial property owners, businesses, and contractors. Our area of expertise is concrete waterproofing, soil stabilization and concrete restoration. More specifically our main specialty is ground water control by injection of polyurethane grouts and epoxy injection resins to stop leaks, stabilize soils and protect and strengthen concrete structures.
